{"tid":450388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府聘青年入中策組　月薪最高9.5萬","createTime":"2017-10-28T06:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T07:41:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f0602ad21ccfe4cd377bfdea3501edf1a0301271","tid":450388,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:40:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171028/20197071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171028%2F20197071&d=ttNQWDG3zbjj93Fe4ww0CWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=c073dd9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171028%2F20197071&h=4690d16f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171028/20197071</a><br />\n<br />\n政府聘青年入中策組　月薪最高9.5萬<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥提出改組中央政策組為「政策創新與統籌辦事處」（政統辦）。中策組昨刊登廣告，招聘「政策及項目統籌主任」及「高級政策及項目統籌主任」，後者月薪6萬元起，較政務主任（AO）起薪點高逾萬元，最高年薪更可達114萬元。但林鄭日前表示有關職位會聘請約20至30名年輕人，有年齡歧視之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n政策及項目統籌主任及高級政策及項目統籌主任屬非公務員職位，合約期3年，前者月薪3萬至4.8萬元，後者6萬至9.5萬元。<br />\n<br />\n連同約滿酬金，高級主任3年總薪酬最高可達約400萬元。職位共20至30個空缺，職責為公共政策研究及分析、協助統籌跨局政策，申請人需持大學學位或同等學歷，持有最少兩年政策研究及公共事務等工作經驗，高級主任一職更需達5年。兩職位即日起接受申請，下月17日截止。<br />\n<br />\n今次招聘廣告列明，應徵者須撰寫一份中文或英文申請信，列出申請原因及專長等，沒有提交者不獲考慮。中策組下月7日會在政府總部設招聘簡介會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171028/large/1026yik1002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171028%2Flarge%2F1026yik1002.jpg&h=1d1f89f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭曾表示有關職位會聘請20至30位年輕人，被外界質疑有年齡歧視之嫌。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘇敬恆未表明會否申請<br />\n<br />\n雖然招聘廣告沒列出申請年齡規定，但林鄭本月12日發表施政報告已表明會吸納有志從事政策研究的青年加入。日前她再表示將招聘約20至30名年輕人出任上述職位，似有年齡歧視之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n理大社會政策研究中心主任鍾劍華認為，招聘廣告沒列出年齡上限，理應任何合資格者均可申請，若因年齡因素拒絕聘請，或引起投訴甚至司法覆核。至於疑因建制派不滿而失落食物及衞生局政治助理一職的《城市論壇》主持蘇敬恆，沒正面回應會否申請。中策組回應指，若申請人符合入職條件、具備良好能力和經驗，不會因為其年齡因素而拒絕聘用。<br />\n<br />\n■記者王家文<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171028/large/a1004a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171028%2Flarge%2Fa1004a.gif&h=b780d2ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f35904d614e189531e4e9edd49aa8e8aeb54c2e","tid":450388,"uid":61280,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:42:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">其實正名!&quot;中賊組&quot;已經足夠！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"647316b6dcf2c93970ec442514602e000e12a286","tid":450388,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zfju8h4i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzfju8h4i&h=74cb28b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b79e5631e46891e565707ffb71ea9c2bf6a961b","tid":450388,"uid":2169,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:50:01.000Z","msg":"正呀 呢個真係德政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3年已經夠買樓"},{"pid":"d1b588b85fde3018a03433ccb3d281d783632d8e","tid":450388,"uid":134864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:52:33.000Z","msg":"沖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狂奶鞋底"},{"pid":"e4609e0c814e2d7f690af532524b4cf44e767488","tid":450388,"uid":56546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:54:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正呀 呢個真係德政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3年已經夠買樓</blockquote><br />\n平平地嘅話一年都夠<img src=\"/assets/